      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"كُلْ مِنَ اَلسَّمَكِ مَا كَانَ لَهُ فُلُوسٌ وَ لاَ تَأْكُلْ مِنْهُ مَا لَيْسَ لَهُ فَلْسٌ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4152 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Eat from the fish that has scales, and do not eat from it that which has no scales.\""
        ]
      }
